{"tid":2438067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：百多至二百名公務員無簽聲明　或安排離職","createTime":"2021-03-08T09:07:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T09:38:12.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90b09ca2c21aafeb91644bc04f54b95cb294c5c4","tid":2438067,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:07:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579405-20210308.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579405-20210308.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv0WuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=ee3fdaf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579405-20210308.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7388ea9e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579405-20210308.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權表示，暫時有100多至200名公務員沒有簽署宣誓聲明，至於所屬部門分布如何，現時未能掌握，當局下月會到立法會的事務委員會交代。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權重申，如有公務員拒絕簽署聲明，當局會啟動相關機制跟進，包括了解原因。他說，若公務員拒絕簽署聲明以接納及承擔基本責任，政府會對有關人士失去信心，因此會按機制跟進，或安排有關人士離開公務員隊伍。"},{"pid":"152a24ad7582168244801bd70da6d4069257dd5e","tid":2438067,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:07:17.000Z","msg":"真義士！<br />\n<br />\n英國見！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54181b8942235162dfb674fa5ba9595a26a37d32","tid":2438067,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:08:44.000Z","msg":"之後應該仲有一批會走"},{"pid":"7a97d5e4d37b3f7c94c3049ef77e2a9c6cae1e8f","tid":2438067,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:10:17.000Z","msg":"Thanks 真義士！"},{"pid":"ea24d3648f3dd00d98f122dea0fe2ec569901e4c","tid":2438067,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T09:38:12.000Z","msg":"聽講堅多資深嘅走，大家都怕秋後算賬"}]}